  <thing id="xDKniAbBla" name="Abyssal Blast" description="Once per day, a death knight can unleash a blast of eldritch fire. The blast fills a 20 ft radius spread anywhere within a range of 400 +40 feet per HD of the death knight. The blast deals 1d6 damage per HD (max 20d6), half of which is fire and half of which is divine power and not subject to being reduced by {i}protection from energy{/i} or similar spells/abilities. Targets who succeed on a Ref save (DC 10 + 1/2 death knight HD + Cha mod) take half damage." compset="Special" summary="Blast of abyssal fire in Long range, 1/2 dam is divine power (Ref half).">
