  <thing id="cdMedEmpow" name="Power of Meditation" description="Once per day, you may cast one spell as though it had the Empower Spell feat applied to it. However, you cast the spell at its normal level, not at two levels higher, and use the normal casting time of the spell. You need not know the Empower Spell feat to use this ability." compset="Special" summary="Cast a spell as though it were Empowered for free 1/day">
