  <thing id="cdTreaDLCS" name="Treachery" description="{b}Diety:{/b} Hiddukel\n\n{b}Granted Power:{/b} Once per day, when you attack a flat-footed opponent, you can deal additional damage equal to 1d6 per 2 cleric levels you possess (round up, not down in this case) with a single melee attack. You must declare that you are using this ability before making the attack, and if you miss the opponent that use of your power is wasted. Creatures immune to critical hits are also immune to this additional damage.\n\n{b}Treachery Domain Spells{/b}\n {b}1{/b}   Undetectable alignment\n {b}2{/b}   Eagle&apos;s splendor\n {b}3{/b}   Bestow curse\n {b}4{/b}   Glibness\n {b}5{/b}   Magic jar\n {b}6{/b}   Symbol of persuasion\n {b}7{/b}   Eyebite\n {b}8{/b}   Trap the soul\n {b}9{/b}   Imprisonment" compset="ClerDomain" uniqueness="unique">
