  <thing id="sDInsTStri" name="True Strike" description="You gain temporary, intuitive insight into the immediate future during your next attack. Your next single attack roll (if it is made before the end of the next round) gains a +20 insight bonus. Additionally, you are not affected by the miss chance that applies to attackers trying to strike a concealed target.\n\n{i}Focus{/i}: A small wooden replica of an archery target." compset="Spell" summary="+20 on your next attack roll.">
