  <thing id="sDLibRemFe" name="Remove Fear" description="You instill courage in the subject, granting it a +4 morale bonus against {i}fear{/i} effects for 10 minutes. If the subject is under the influence of a {i}fear{/i} effect when receiving the spell, that effect is suppressed for the duration of the spell. {b}It affects one creature, plus one additional creature per four levels, no two of which can be more than 30 ft. apart.{/b}\n\n{i}Remove fear{/i} counters and dispels {i}cause fear{/i}." compset="Spell" summary="Suppresses fear or gives +4 on saves against fear for one subject + one per four levels.">
