  <thing id="sDLibRemPa" name="Remove Paralysis" description="You can free one or more creatures from the effects of any temporary paralysis or related magic, including a ghoul&#146;s touch or a slow spell. If the spell is cast on one creature, the paralysis is negated. If cast on two creatures, each receives another save with a +4 resistance bonus against the effect that afflicts it. If cast on three or four creatures, each receives another save with a +2 resistance bonus.\n\nThe spell does not restore ability scores reduced by penalties, damage, or drain." compset="Spell" summary="Frees one or more creatures from paralysis or slow effect.">
