  <thing id="cDrRDFeat2" name="Dragon Feats" description="A dragon rider can grant his dragon cohort the full benefits of a second bonus feat chosen from the following list: Cleave, Flyby Attack, Hover, Improved Initiative, Improved Sunder, Power Attack, Quicken Spell-Like Ability, Snatch, Strafing Breath, Weapon Focus, of WIngover\n\nThe bonus feat does not count against the dragon&apos;s normal feat capacity, though it must still meet any prerequisites noted in the feat description. The dragon rider must spend one week training with his dragon in order for it to recieve the bonus feat." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Dragon cohort gains listed bonus feat from training with rider." sortorder="5">
