  <thing id="cDrREmpCom" name="Empathic Communication" description="A dragon rider is able to use nonverbal communication with his dragon to convey information and instructions as long as they are within sight of each other." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Pass info/instructions nonverbally while in sight of dragon cohort." sortorder="3">
