  <thing id="cDrRInFear" name="Inspire Fear" description="The dragon rider adds his class levels to his dragon cohort&apos;s HD when determining the DC of the dragon&apos;s frightful presence ability. The range of the dragon&apos;s frightful presence is calculated as if the dragon were one age catagory higher." compset="ClSpecial" summary="+6 to dragon&apos;s HD for frightful presence DC, range as 1 age cat older." sortorder="6">
