  <thing id="cDrRDirAtt" name="Directed Attack" description="The dragon rider may give encouragement and direct his dragon cohort&apos;s attacks. Directing the dragon is a full-round action that does not provoke attacks of opportunity. When directed, the dragon gains a +4 circumstance bonus on its attack rolls." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Full rd, give dragon cohort +4 circ bonus to hit." sortorder="7">
