  <thing id="cDrRDefTac" name="Defensive Tactics" description="Neither the dragon rider nor his dragon cohort can be flanked while the dragon rider is in the saddle. The dragon and rider have learned to look in each other&apos;s &quot;blind spots&quot; to prevent enemies from sneaking up on them." compset="ClSpecial" summary="While mounted, rider and dragon are immune to flanking." sortorder="8">
