  <thing id="xMirPortal" name="Mirror Portals" description="At will, a fetch can create a two-way portal connecting the Abys to a reflective surface on the Material Plane, such as a mirror or a pool of water. This is similar to the {i}gate{/i} spell, but only the fetch and any objects it carries can pass through the mirror portal. The reflective surface must be large enough for the fetch to pass through (a minimum of 2 1/2 feet on a side). The fetch can use the reflective surface even if it is not reflecting anything (for instance, if it is in a dark room).\n\nThe portal is initially latent. The fetch can see and hear into the Material Plane" compset="Special">
