  <thing id="cInqEFocus" name="Extreme Focus" description="An inquisitor must be able to ignore outside distractions while following up a lead, for fear of missing an important detail. Once per day per level of the inquisitor, he may add his ranks in Concentration to any one Intelligence- or Wisdom-based skill check." compset="ClSpecial" summary="X/day, add Concentration ranks as bonus to Int or Wis based skill checks." sortorder="1">
