  <thing id="cInqImpUnD" name="Improved Uncanny Dodge" description="At 6th level, the inquisitor can no longer be flanked, since he can react to multiple opponents as easily as he can react to a single attacker. This defense denies the rogue&#146;s ability to use flank attacks to do a sneak attack on the inquisitor. The exception to this defense is that a rogue at least 4 levels higher than the inquisitor can flank the investigator (and thus sneak attack)." compset="ClSpecial" summary="You can no longer be flanked." sortorder="6">
