  <thing id="ioDiskMish" name="Disks of Mishakal" description="The knowledge of the true gods of Good is contained within these sacred disks. Anyone reading the disks may learn of the gods of Good and may choose a good aligned god as a patron deity.\n\nOnly good creatures may examine the sacred disks safely. If a neutral creature touches the disks, it immediately suffers 2d6 points of holy (good) damage. If an evil creature touches the disks, it immediately suffers 4d6 points of holy (good) damage.\n\nStrong divination and evocation (good); CL 20th" compset="Wondrous" uniqueness="unique">
