  <thing id="sMysSumNa8" name="Summon Nature&apos;s Ally VIII" description="This spell functions like {i}summon nature&#146;s ally I{/i}, except that you can summon one 8th-level creature, 1d3 7th-level creatures {b}(no two of which can be more than 30 ft. apart){/b} of the same kind, or 1d4+1 lower-level creatures of the same kind.\n\nWhen you use a summoning spell to summon an air, chaotic, earth, evil, fire, good, lawful, or water creature, it is a spell of that type.\n\n{b}Summon Nature&#146;s Ally{/b}\n{b}8th Level{/b}\nDire shark1\nRoc\nSalamander, noble [NE]\nTojanida, elder\n\n{b}7th Level{/b}\nArrowhawk, elder\nDire tiger\nElemental, greater (any)\nDjinni (genie) [NG]\nInvisible stalker\nPixie* (sprite) [NG; with sleep arrows]\nSquid, giant1 (animal)\nTriceratops (dinosaur)\nTyrannosaurus (dinosaur)\nWhale, cachalot1 (animal)\nXorn, elder\n*Can&#146;t cast {i}Otto&#146;s irresistible dance{/i}\n\n{b}6th Level{/b}\nDire bear\nElemental, Huge (any)\nElephant (animal)\nGirallon\nMegaraptor (dinosaur)\nOctopus, giant1 (animal)\nPixie* (sprite) [NG; no special arrows]\nSalamander, average [NE]\nWhale, baleen1\nXorn, average\n*Can&#146;t cast {i}Otto&#146;s irresistible dance{/i}\n1 May be summoned only into an aquatic or watery environment." compset="Spell" summary="Calls creature to fight.">
