  <thing id="sMysStones" name="Stoneskin" description="The warded creature gains resistance to blows, cuts, stabs, and slashes. The subject gains damage reduction 10/adamantine. (It ignores the first 10 points of damage each time it takes damage from a weapon, though an adamantine weapon bypasses the reduction.) Once the spell has prevented a total of 10 points of damage per caster level (maximum 150 points), it is discharged.\n\n{i}Material Component{/i}: Granite and 250 gp worth of diamond dust sprinkled on the target&#146;s skin." compset="Spell" summary="Ignore 10 points of damage per attack.">
