  <thing id="sMysHalUnd" name="Halt Undead" description="This spell renders as many as three undead creatures {b}(no two of which can be more than 30 ft. apart){/b} immobile. A non-intelligent undead creature (such as a skeleton or zombie) gets no saving throw; an intelligent undead creature does. If the spell is successful, it renders the undead creature immobile for the duration of the spell (similar to the effect of {i}hold person{/i} on a living creature). The effect is broken if the {i}halted{/i} creatures are attacked or take damage.\n\n{i}Material Component{/i}: A pinch of sulfur and powdered garlic." compset="Spell" summary="Immobilizes undead for 1 round/level.">
