  <thing id="sMysWeird" name="Weird" description="This spell functions like {i}phantasmal killer{/i}, except it can affect more than one creature {b}(any number of creatures, no two of which can be more than 30 ft. apart){/b}. Only the affected creatures see the phantasmal creatures attacking them, though you see the attackers as shadowy shapes.\n\nIf a subject&#146;s Fortitude save succeeds, it still takes 3d6 points of damage and is stunned for 1 round. The subject also takes 1d4 points of temporary Strength damage." compset="Spell" summary="Fearful illusion affects all within 30 ft., either killing or dealing 3d6 damage.">
