  <thing id="cdTreacher" name="Treacherous Backstab" description="Once per day, when you attack a flat-footed opponent, you can deal additional damage equal to 1d6 per two mystic levels you possess (round up, not down, in this case) with a single melee attack. You must declare that you are using this ability before making the attack, and if you miss the opponent that use of your power is wasted. Creatures immune to critical hits are also immune to this additional damage." compset="Special" summary="1/day, deal extra damage against flat footed foe.">
