  <thing id="cNblConf" name="Inspire Confidence 1/day" description="Beginning at 2nd level, a noble can use oratory to inspire confidence in allies, bolstering them and improving their chances of success. An ally must listen to and observe the noble for a full round for the inspiration to take hold. The effects last for 5 rounds. The noble can inspire a number of allies equal to half his noble levels, rounded up.\n\nAn ally inspired with confidence gains a +2 morale bonus on saving throws and a +1 morale bonus on attack and weapon damage rolls.\n\nThe noble can&#146;t inspire confidence in himself. The ability only aids his allies." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Grants allies +1 to attack and damage rolls and +2 to all saves.">
