  <thing id="cNblGreat" name="Inspire Greatness (1 ally)" description="Beginning at 11th level, a noble can inspire greatness in an ally, granting extra fighting capability. This works similar to inspire confidence, except it affects but a single ally. An ally inspired with greatness gains +2d6 temporary hit points, a +2 competence bonus on attacks, and a +2 morale bonus on saving throws. The effect lasts for 5 rounds. The noble can inspire greatness once per day. For every three levels beyond 11th, the noble can inspire greatness in one additional ally.\n\nThe noble can&#146;t inspire greatness in himself. The ability only aids his allies." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Grants 1 ally 2d6 temp hit points, +2 to attacks and +2 to all saves.">
